{"TopicId":168547,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"What\u0026#039;s with Imgur?","CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-14T22:07:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-14T22:07:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s literally the only image hosting service we can use here, and it has no problems with it. Why the heck were all these problems caused, and why was it blocked in the first place?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-14T22:20:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat problems?\u00A0 I see people using it every day in the massive old \u0027what did you do today\u0027 thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you mean \u0027why is imgur the only host which still works\u0027, imgur was actually created just for hosting images.\u00A0 Most other sites aren\u0027t actually image hosters, and see image hotlinking as parasitism.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-14T22:26:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223244549\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221513289276\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s literally the only image hosting service we can use here\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s literally not true.\u00A0 I have hundreds of images on the forum and have never used Imgur in my life.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-14T23:08:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can use any image hosting site really.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfaik the only thing broken about Imgur is the albums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can even copy paste the link from Steam and use that if you play on there, that\u0027s what I do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Piatzin","CreatedById":166940,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-16T22:24:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI only use Imgur for Kerbalx\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOtherwise, I use Flickr and Cubeupload\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-16T23:30:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoving to Kerbal Network, since this is about the forum and not KSP itself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs others have pointed out, 1. imgur works just fine, and 2. so does everywhere else.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s nothing special about imgur.\u00A0 It just happens to be the overwhelmingly most common hosting site here, due to convenience, popularity, etc. But you can use any site you like, as long as the images are publicly linkable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-19T12:58:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny progress getting albums to work? It\u0027s been a while.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-05T12:22:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223299010\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221519045089\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim!\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 02/19/2018 at 1:58 PM, Majorjim! said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny progress getting albums to work? It\u0027s been a while.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHellooo? Anyone know if this will ever get fixed or is this part of the slow death of this website? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dafni","CreatedById":149636,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-05T12:37:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223310590\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520252554\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim!\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Majorjim! said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHellooo? Anyone know if this will ever get fixed or is this part of the slow death of this website? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably, and sadly, the latter. Hope to get proven otherwise.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-05T14:41:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223310605\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520253458\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149636\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dafni\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Dafni said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably, and sadly, the latter. Hope to get proven otherwise.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgreed....\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nImgur album embedding was one of the nice features. Now its just easier to link the album.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal101","CreatedById":157058,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-05T15:46:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts possible to get almost the same results sans scrolling feature. When you hold [Ctrl] when clicking on the image with RMB, there is an \u0022Edit\u0022 submenu.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWithin that submenu, its possible to resize the image precisely and also make it clickable. If you link it this way to the album, you can show several images with hotlinking to album on imgur.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThis ^^^ method is very unlikely to break \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-05T22:23:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/Vo9mu\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ThisIsJustATest\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022410\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/IckzUMCg.png\u0022 style=\u0022width:728px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u0022728\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223310771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520264795\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157058\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbal101\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Kerbal101 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts possible to get almost the same results sans scrolling feature. When you hold [Ctrl] when clicking on the image with RMB, there is an \u0022Edit\u0022 submenu.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWithin that submenu, its possible to resize the image precisely and also make it clickable. If you link it this way to the album, you can show several images with hotlinking to album on imgur.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThis ^^^ method is very unlikely to break \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike that?\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\ni mean, yeah, I could. But you still have to go to an external page in the end anyways. So why not just stick a link somewhere?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-06T04:58:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223310590\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520252554\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Majorjim!\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, Majorjim! said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHellooo? Anyone know if this will ever get fixed or is this part of the slow death of this website? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo one is currently working on this. Our current moderating team does not have expertise in whatever issue is causing the problem, and to be honest, it\u0027s not a terribly productive use of our time since Imgur just keeps breaking\u00A0our fixes and work-arounds anyway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T13:44:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223311310\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520312307\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 03/06/2018 at 5:58 AM, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo one is currently working on this. Our current moderating team does not have expertise in whatever issue is causing the problem, and to be honest, it\u0027s not a terribly productive use of our time since Imgur just keeps breaking\u00A0our fixes and work-arounds anyway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOuch, that\u0027s a real shame. Does anyone know any other way to display image albums here? Perhaps using another site?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T17:00:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\nApparently, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/61954-majorjim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002261954\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/61954-majorjim/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Majorjim!\u003C/a\u003E, it is an IMGUR issue. The album I just tried to share was my DC-10 album... and it didn\u0027t work.\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022//imgur.com/a/4h26d\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/4h26d\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022//imgur.com/a/4h26d\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EAlbum a/4h26d will appear when post is submitted\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n-----\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\nOk, Edit update: I can post the links to the album directly, but it does not do the automatic embed.\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\nI tried using the button to link the image, but apparently there is an issue with the scripting for the button because it links to an image, not an album. And the image address is the same as the album address with the exception of the directory identifier /a/albumnumber.\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\nI am trying a third way...\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/4h26d\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022yVBpGUJ.png?1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022704\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/yVBpGUJ.png?1\u0022 style=\u0022width:924px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221022\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\nEdit 2:\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\nNo, using an image to link to the album doesn\u0027t work either...\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;blockquote\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atn\u0022\u003Eclass\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atv\u0022\u003E\u0022imgur-embed-pub\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atn\u0022\u003Elang\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atv\u0022\u003E\u0022en\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atn\u0022\u003Edata-id\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atv\u0022\u003E\u0022a/4h26d\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026gt;\u0026lt;a\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atn\u0022\u003Ehref\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atv\u0022\u003E\u0022//imgur.com/4h26d\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EKSP DC-10\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/blockquote\u0026gt;\u0026lt;script\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atn\u0022\u003Easync\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atn\u0022\u003Esrc\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atv\u0022\u003E\u0022//s.imgur.com/min/embed.js\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atn\u0022\u003Echarset\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022atv\u0022\u003E\u0022utf-8\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022tag\u0022\u003E\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/script\u0026gt;\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-03-08T17:11:55Z\u0022 title=\u002203/08/2018 05:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 8, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by adsii1970\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-09T03:09:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223313475\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520528458\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, using an image to link to the album doesn\u0027t work either...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can click the image to the album. Not sure if thats what you meant?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-15T04:46:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImgur is sadly (stupendously) blocked over the mobile network here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI simply use Dropboxes\u0027 usercontent URL.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-16T12:34:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo any other image sites allow for albums?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Archgeek","CreatedById":116048,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-05T22:17:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223310771\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168547\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520264795\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157058\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbal101\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/5/2018 at 9:46 AM, Kerbal101 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts possible to get almost the same results sans scrolling feature. When you hold [Ctrl] when clicking on the image with RMB, there is an \u0022Edit\u0022 submenu.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWithin that submenu, its possible to resize the image precisely and also make it clickable. If you link it this way to the album, you can show several images with hotlinking to album on imgur.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThis ^^^ method is very unlikely to break \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for that information. \u00A0That \u0022Insert other media\u0022 =\u0026gt; from URL =\u0026gt; imgur_url.png =\u0026gt; ctrl\u002BRMB =\u0026gt; Edit =\u0026gt; link URL = imgur/a/album path is probably the closest thing we have to a working album embed these days. \u00A0Not quite as nice as what we had, and tricky in that you need to add the image file extension,\u00A0but at least you can pick a link image to serve as the thumbnail of sorts for the album link, plus nicely control its display size and/or shove it in a spoiler.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drew Kerman","CreatedById":103177,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-17T23:22:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just noticed a complete change to the style of the Imgur gallery embeds used in my weekly ops posts on the KSA website, so they recently updated something. I don\u0027t have time right now to test anything here so just giving a heads up to anyone that wants to fiddle with imgur embeds and see if they work now\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}